<p>The Theatre Museum grew out of the private theatre archive of the Düsseldorf Dumont-Lindemann Actors’ Association
  (1904 - 1933); the archive was founded in 1938. It was donated to the City of Düsseldorf by Gustaf Lindemann in 1947.
